的過去<br />\n<br />\n曾經收起的抱擁<br />\n曾經懶去寄 的書信<br />\n留到葬禮那一刻已是無用<br />\n墓碑的旁邊 我即使向你談論今天的鎖碎<br />\n你都不覆半句<br />\n<br />\n若當天孩子 懂得將我愛你這一句<br />\n豁出去<br />\n或會拉近差距"},{"pid":"540373b64c8507977ec2be3293cad13dcdf9264d","tid":224062,"uid":47451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T01:29:15.000Z","msg":"Shirley 古巨基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"447d9a95a5c33adb8ef68c323c17fdbec870dd68","tid":224062,"uid":110423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:23:05.000Z","msg":"他一個人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f634d5f8b06f7fe254c80b4aebd71dbdbb1e3d58","tid":224062,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:24:55.000Z","msg":"活著多好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n遊玩時開心一點不必掛念我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b255910fd96000ee3e879d19c75db7c2b9aaeea","tid":224062,"uid":38476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"You're beautiful. It's true.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a635e02fbdcbb40311b25ac8fb35bf11ea83a419","tid":224062,"uid":53972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"寧願失戀亦不想失禮 難道要對着你力歇聲嘶<br />\n即使不抵 都要眼閉<br />\n我這種身世 有甚麼資格 獻世<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715f84eb4b94756266d8959046e52a767a07c9b3","tid":224062,"uid":95516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T08:02:08.000Z","msg":"Say anything<br />\nEndless rain<br />\nWithout you"},{"pid":"e28eaa80